{"tid":2160790,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"講真 搞乜保就業都係假 我地目的就係搞到所有中資全部執笠","createTime":"2020-08-17T07:50:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-17T08:03:22.000Z","uid":84408,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"bdac2a2a30650b04fc248c95b2cd3501f7009f29","tid":2160790,"uid":84408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T07:50:24.000Z","msg":"楊明間舖客仔都唔多個仲未執得<br />\n惠康 黨鐵呢啲全部比人壟斷哂<br />\n講真經濟咁差佢都未死唔去<br />\n就知佢地資源有幾多<br />\n藍店一日唔執 經濟又點可能轉型？<br />\n<br />\n黃店都唔好咁老定 雖然係同路人<br />\n但剝削人係絕對嘅壞事<br />\n好似琴日膳心小館單野咁<br />\n<br />\n香港人成場運動 就係想爭取自由停止剝削<br />\n希望黃店自己唔好本末倒置"},{"pid":"8dd40f6dfb741f2148f8c319e859287cc781a112","tid":2160790,"uid":84408,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T07:52:39.000Z","msg":"中資一日唔執笠<br />\n香港繼續做洗黑錢基地<br />\n金融藥房狗全面進場 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11a372463f0acd4040140bcf1bae1be71525deb7","tid":2160790,"uid":84408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T07:57:25.000Z","msg":"自推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf4593ced53163b4646e104625a2a458af530215","tid":2160790,"uid":35924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T07:57:50.000Z","msg":"但黃店死哂都未到中資死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcc1255f79577717496481cb19efb9ee24582546","tid":2160790,"uid":84408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bf4593ced53163b4646e104625a2a458af530215","tid":2160790,"uid":35924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T07:57:50.000Z","msg":"但黃店死哂都未到中資死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/ass